videos.description: Braxton Key puts Alabama up 9-6 as he finishes with the nice move in the paint.
videos.headline: Key with the nice move in the lane for the layup

videos.description: Avery Johnson Jr. banks the ball high off the glass as he makes the tough layup.
videos.headline: Alabama's Johnson Jr. uses the glass to get the awkward layup to fall

videos.description: Alabama head coach Avery Johnson talks about the Crimson Tide's first half against South Carolina.
videos.headline: Halftime Interview: Avery Johnson

videos.description: Crimson Tide guard Dazon Ingram passes to teammate Donta Hall for the layup, plus the foul.
videos.headline: Alabama's Ingram finds Hall with the nice pass for the 3-point play

videos.description: Rakym Felder deflects Alabama's inbound pass to teammate Duane Notice, who finds PJ Dozier for the slam.
videos.headline: Felder's steal leads to dunk for South Carolina

videos.description: Great ball movement by the Crimson Tide ends with Jimmie Taylor finding Braxton Key for the slam.
videos.headline: Great passing by Alabama leads to dunk from Key

videos.description: Sindarius Thornwell's big defensive play leads to a circus lay-in on the offensive end.
videos.headline: South Carolina's Thornwell comes up with the big steal that leads to the tough layup, plus the foul

videos.description: Alabama mascot Big Al gets into a little back and forth with a service dog at the Alabama-South Carolina game.
videos.headline: Alabama's Big Al gets into it with service dog

videos.description: Braxton Key drives and dishes to Riley Norris, who gets the layup to fall late.
videos.headline: Norris' late layup increases Alabama's lead
